videos.headline: Ehlinger passes Vince Young in Texas record books with TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger completes a 25-yard touchdown pass to Roschon Johnson to pass Vince Young for 5th most passing touchdowns in Texas history.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger passes Vince Young in Texas record books with TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Smith for 53-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger hits Jake Smith in stride to score a 53-yard Texas touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger finds Smith for 53-yard TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingram runs 26 yards for Texas TD
videos.description: Keaontay Ingram takes off to score a 26-yard Texas touchdown to give them a 21-0 lead over Rice.

videos.headline: Ehlinger and Smith connect for another Texas TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger and Jake Smith complete their second touchdown connection as Smith reaches the end zone for a 12-yard score to extend Texas' lead.
